prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D cartoon illustration for a birthday greeting card front cover, in a detailed botanical illustration style. In the center, two people are depicted from the waist up. The first person is a young East Asian woman in her early 20s, with long, straight black hair parted in the middle, wearing thin-rimmed round glasses and a light blue crewneck sweatshirt with a circular white and blue graphic on the chest. She is smiling warmly at the camera. The second person is a young East Asian/Southeast Asian man in his early 20s with short, slightly tousled black hair, standing behind the woman and hugging her from behind. He is wearing a tan hoodie and has a big, happy smile. They are both surrounded by a humorous and chaotic arrangement of botanical elements: mischievous Venus flytraps are comically trying to nibble on the corners of the frame, and a few slightly wilted, droopy flowers are mixed in with vibrant, elegant blossoms like peonies and roses, as if they've partied a little too hard. The overall background is a soft, off-white. In the safe center area, elegantly lettered in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The scene is lighthearted, funny, and full of natural, soft organic shapes. Unique ID: 1af2d10f-b30e-44b7-8184-0a7a482d29a2.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
